Class MusicTrack

  • java.lang.Object
    • dj2.core.MusicTrack
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MusicTrack
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is the MusicTrack Class, it has got all the information about a music track plus it adds automatically it self to mostRecentlyPlayedList if it is played.
